      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EEBEEBEE (2) ran second last start at Bendigo over 2150m, beaten 13 metres. Has the benefit of a good draw and is good enough to take out a race like this. CAPITAL AVENUE (5) is a four-year-old mare by Captain Crunch from Nicki Rocks on debut. Trial winner who looks above average. Well-placed to score at her first appearance. DIAMONDONTHEROCKS (6) is worth another chance after a last-start eighth over 2150m at Bendigo two weeks ago. Can bounce back. WATCH HIM DANCE (3) found form and finished in the money two runs ago then came back to earth when he broke and finished fifth last start over 1700m at Horsham, coming home 5.5 metres from the winner. Likely to get all the favours from this nice draw and rates a live chance in a similar assignment.",
